Norsk Hydro A/S &lt;NHY.O> is issuing 50mln stg bonds due April 15, 1993 carrying a 9-7/8 pct couponand priced at 101-5/8, said Hambros Bank Ltd as lead manager.    Norsk Hydro is 51 pct owned by the Kingdom of Norway. Thebonds, which are available in denominations of 1,000 and 10,000stg will be listed on the London Stock Exchange.    Payment date is April 15. Fees consist of a 1-1/4 pctselling concession and 5/8 pct combined management andunderwriting. REUITER&#3;